# Codex Collab Settings Example

Copy this file to `.claude/codex-collab.local.md` and customize for your project.

---
model: o4-mini
sandbox: read-only

# Timeout settings
codex:
  wait_timeout: 180        # seconds (default: 180, max: 600)

# Launch mode settings (how Codex is launched)
launch:
  mode: auto               # auto | wt | tmux | inline
                           # auto: tmuxセッション内→tmux, それ以外→wt→inline
                           # tmux: 現在のtmuxセッション内に新しいウィンドウを作成
                           # inline: 現在のターミナルで実行（ブロッキング）

# Planning exchange settings (Codex plans → Claude questions → Codex refines)
exchange:
  enabled: true              # Global kill-switch for planning exchanges
  max_iterations: 3
  user_confirm: on_important # never | always | on_important
  history_mode: summarize    # full | summarize

# Review iteration settings (Codex reviews → Claude fixes → Codex re-reviews)
review:
  enabled: true              # Enable/disable review iterations
  max_iterations: 5          # Can be higher than exchange (goal is clear, diff is small)
  user_confirm: never        # Auto-iterate for reviews
---

